OL,3,C'I was in terrible pain' - grandmother
OL,4,Cwaits 14 hours for ambulance
OL,6,FAn 82-year-old woman from Cornwall had
OL,7,Fto wait 14 hours for an ambulance in
OL,8,F'terrible pain' after she dislocated
OL,9,Fher hip at home.
OL,11,FThe accident happened in January 2024
OL,12,Fwhen Liz Brockhurst called for an
OL,13,Fambulance.
OL,15,FShe told ITV News West Country: "I
OL,16,Fended up being there from six in the
OL,17,Fevening to 8.30am when the ambulance
OL,18,Feventually arrived.
