OL,3,C'I was in terrible pain' - grandmother
OL,4,Cwaits 14 hours for ambulance
OL,6,FShe said: "I can't emphasise enough
OL,7,Fhow brilliant they all are.
OL,9,F"They were all lovely and they all
OL,10,Fworked so hard. So I have absolutely
OL,11,Fnothing to say against the hospital
OL,12,Fstaff of any sort.
OL,14,F"The system is wrong. There's
OL,15,Fsomething very, very wrong about
OL,16,Fhaving to wait - Not just me, but
OL,17,Feverybody - having to wait such a long
OL,18,Fwhile for any medical treatments."JLiz
OL,19,Fsays she is 'petrified' of suffering
OL,20,Fanother injury and having to endure
OL,21,Fanother long wait.
