OL,3,C'I was in terrible pain' - grandmother
OL,4,Cwaits 14 hours for ambulance
OL,6,FBoth South Western Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fand the Royal Cornwall Hospital Trust
OL,8,Fhave apologised for the delays in
OL,9,FLiz's treatment.
OL,11,FSouth West Ambulance Service said they
OL,12,Fhad improved the numbers of hours
OL,13,Fambulances are on the road each week.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Royal Cornwall
OL,16,FHospitals NHS Trust said: "The delays
OL,17,Frepresent pressure not only on the
OL,18,Fmain emergency department but across
OL,19,Fthe entire health and care system.
