OL,6,F"We have seen growing demand since the
OL,7,Fstart of this year and throughout the
OL,8,Ftime we were in a system critical
OL,9,Fincident."
OL,11,FThey added that they are offering more
OL,12,Fcare in the community to try and
OL,13,Freduce the demand on hospitals.
